{"tid":635774,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實咁樣係咪可以叫房處收番間屋？","createTime":"2018-04-20T10:31:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-21T09:38:14.000Z","uid":13674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b124fd5f74ca63a6438e7c17c8ceafe103b66448","tid":635774,"uid":13674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T10:31:54.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟住公屋，隔離住咗個有精神分裂嘅肥婆<br />\n佢一個人住，平時間唔中佢個妹會探下佢<br />\n平日大家都無乜交流，係細細個搬入黎果陣會去佢屋企玩下鋼琴（果時唔知佢有病）<br />\n其實平日大家都相安無事，但係佢有個壞習慣<br />\n就係唔多願意覆診拎藥<br />\n所以由細到大，間唔中就會唔見咗一段時間<br />\n大咗至知，佢無食藥發癲，比人捉咗入去精神病院<br />\n（最誇張果次係要岀動警察同消防員，樓下仲鋪哂氣塾）<br />\n好啦問題黎啦，今日係樓下拎信果時見到隔離屋個信箱爆哂，就醒起個女人好似兩年前比人捉咗入去之後就無番過黎，姐係間屋掉空咗兩年<br />\n既然係咁可唔可以叫人收番間屋？<br />\n佢咁樣又入又岀都唔係辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ea8b1a5bb28edbf58fe42bdf6e3cd33ef7ee2eb","tid":635774,"uid":13674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T14:28:27.000Z","msg":"推一下"},{"pid":"5f79b222ec4c7b80f98fc5525a8a78afb5d042e3","tid":635774,"uid":12757,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9ea8b1a5bb28edbf58fe42bdf6e3cd33ef7ee2eb","tid":635774,"uid":13674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T14:28:27.000Z","msg":"推一下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T14:38:54.000Z","msg":"關你撚事咩 又冇攪到你"},{"pid":"40b1b680d1b0521d34cc71c2a1dcbda34f738ba8","tid":635774,"uid":85307,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T14:41:21.000Z","msg":"比個機會佢<br />\n精神病人返到社區好需要支持<br />\n如果唔到就好易復發 無限loop幾十年"},{"pid":"bc9af00eea81cb3e07724a90dd4a8c6378fb7e0b","tid":635774,"uid":25635,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T14:45:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/linear/tc/global-elements/contact-us/online-form-for-reporting-abuse-of-public-housing-resources/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.housingauthority.gov.hk%2Flinear%2Ftc%2Fglobal-elements%2Fcontact-us%2Fonline-form-for-reporting-abu